0001	Tip: Attacking from the back increases your hit rate!
0002	Tip: Use the different elements to gain an advantage! Refer to the element table during combat!
0003	Tip: Job Lv Up to increase your units' stats and gain new abilities!
0004	Tip: Equip equipment to increase your units' job levels!
0005	Tip: Equipment is consumed upon Job Lv Up!
0006	Tip: Customise Unit Abilities in Ability Setup!
0007	Tip: Evolve a unit to increase its max level and max job level!
0008	Tip: Evolution materials can be found in Golem Games, Goddess Worship and Alchemia Hunt!
0009	Tip: Use Soul Shards to limit break your units!
0010	Tip: Limit break to increase your units' max level limits and unlock more jobs for them!
0011	Tip: Get different Job Tokens at Trial events!
0012	Tip: Master a job by fully equipping your unit at Job Lv 11!
0013	Tip: Use Alchemia Pots to upgrade your equipment!
0014	Tip: Further improve your units with different gear!
0015	Tip: Upgrade your gear to maximize their potential!
0016	Tip: Use ores to upgrade your gear!
0017	Tip: Need More Zeni? Enter the Gold Rush Event Quest!
0018	Tip: Earn more Gems by completing Story Milestones and Daily Missions!
